\id 3JN  
\h 3 JON 
\toc1 3 Jon 
\toc2 3 Jon 
\mt1 3 Jon  
\mt2 Naoa it…ôm tatol k…®s…®l lan it…ôm Jon t…ôm…ôte  
\imt1 N…ôghat…ôn …ôku…ôk…®r r…ôha naoa u 3 Jon  
\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Aposol Jon t…ôm…ôte naoa u.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm Kaius u in et…ôm-iasol kit r…ôha nim…ôfak, k…ôn in t…®tun Jon.  
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* E nian …ôh, i…ôg…ôtun m…®n r…ôha nim…ôfak koatuw…®n ik…®n p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n, k…ôn moat…ôg…ôtun. Net…ômim it…ôm koat…ôto r…ôhalat n…ôg…ôtun…ôn koatos-ip…ôn nagw…ôn…ôn k…ôm ilat, k…ôn moatos-ip…ôn ik…®n r…ôha nap…®l…ôn, k…ôn motasitu elat.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Kaius, in et…ômim kit it…ôm t…ôtasitu e i…ôg…ôtun m…®n it…ôm kotaliw…ôk ik…®n p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n. Jon t…ôm…ôto namnus…ôn kit e nol…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha Kaius, k…ôn Jon t…ôm…ôte naoa u m…ôm…ô ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhan.  
\c 1  
\s1 N…ôtuoun…ôn n…ôghat…ôn  
\p
\v 1 Kaeas, ik piak keike kit. Io, elta\f + \fr 1:1 \ft 2 Jon 1:1\f* r…ôha nim…ôfak, iat…ôte naoa u k…ôm ik. N…®pahrien…ôn u, m…ôm…ô io ekolkeike p…®k ik.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Inu naoa r…ôha aposol Jon, m…ôto in t…ôs…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn in, m…ôto t…ômat…ôhluaig-in in, tahmen-p…ôn …ôm e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm it…ôm in t…ômol e Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r it…ôm Jon T…ôm…ôte.\f*  
\v 2 Piak keike, io en…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô r…ôham n…ômeg…ôh…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n in t…ôw…®r …ôm, k…ôn iat…ôfak m…ôm…ô on…ôs…®m…®s…ôn m…ôtat…®g w…®r …ôm, k…ôn nat…®g…ôn rafin r…ôham ot…ôw…®r.  
\v 3 N…®kik t…ômagien nian em…ôto piatat m…®n neen k…ômotuwa moat…ôn r…ôham n…ôtul …ôskas…®k…ôn o n…®pahrien…ôn ne n…ôk…ôike…ôn r…ôham o naliw…ôk…ôn e n…®pahrien…ôn.\f + \fr 1:3 \ft 2 Jon 1:4\f*  
\v 4 Nian iat…ôto m…ôm…ô nen…ôt…®k m…®n kotaliw…ôk e n…®pahrien…ôn, k…ôn n…®kik t…ôtagien p…®k m…ôrioah tapr…ôk…®s-in nat…®mnat m…®n rafin.   
\s1 Kaias t…ômol w…ôk t…ôw…®r  
\p
\v 5 Piak ru…ôn, ik nat…ôtul …ôskas…®k o nat naka it…ôm ik natol k…ôm piatat m…®n it…ôm koat…®mn…ô, nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô ilat net…ôm ik p…®s…®n.\f + \fr 1:5 \ft Rom 12:13; Hip 13:2\f*  
\v 6 Ilat k…ômotamnus r…ôham nolkeike…ôn …ôp…ôh e nim…ôfak u ik…®n-u. Ik n…ômol-w…®r k…ôm ilat, masitu elat. K…ôn nian okoatuw…®n e r…ôhalat suat…®p, t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô onakasitu elat\f + \fr 1:6 \ft 1 Kor 16:11; 2 Kor 1:16\f* e nol…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike mihin,  
\v 7 m…ôto-inu ilat koataliw…ôk o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Iesu Kristo, k…ôn m…ôsotos…ôn nasitu…ôn kit o net…ôm k…ôsot…ôfak…ôn.  
\v 8 Tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn kitat u, okot…ôk…ôike motasitu e net…ôm kotol n…ôhlan, m…ôm…ô kitat okotos nelm…®tat m…®n kiti…ôh o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn.   
\s1 Tiotrefes ne Temitrias  
\p
\v 9 Em…ôte naoa kit k…ôm nim…ôfak r…ôham, m…ôto Tiotrefes, in tolkeike p…®k m…ôm…ô ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr at…®p in, m…ôm…ô in et…ôm-iasol kit, k…ôn in t…ôs…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn it…®mat.  
\v 10 Ok…ôm…ô io ek…®mn…ô, k…ôn io oekamnus …ôtuat…®p nat…®mnat m…®n neen it…ôm in tatol, ne n…ôn anion…ôn n…®kal…®t…®mat it…ôm in tat…ôn. In s…ôn…ôm…ô t…ôsit…ôn …ôm piatat m…®n muw…®n iman ik…®n, m…ôto tat…ôn-i…ôhau m…®n net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm kotolkeike m…ôm…ô okotit piatat m…®n motuw…®n im…ôlat ik…®n, k…ôn m…ôtahl-iar…ôp ilat e nim…ôfak.   
\p
\v 11 Piak ru…ôn, sos…ôn o nol…ôn rat r…ôha net…ômim, t…ôr…ôk…®n ik. Os …ôm o et…ômim it…ôm r…ôhan nol…ôn t…ôw…®r. ∆èt…ôl…®g-in-tu m…ôm…ô net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm koatol t…ôw…®r, tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô ilat nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n,\f + \fr 1:11 \ft 1 Jon 2:29\f* m…ôto net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm koatol t…ôrat, tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô ilat kot…ôruru Uhg…®n.  
\v 12 M…ôto net…ômim rafin koat…ônuwi Temetrius.\f + \fr 1:12 \ft 1 Tim 3:7\f* K…ôn r…ôhan nol…ôn m…®n u nian rafin kot…ôg…ôtun m…®n m…ôm…ô tat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn n…ôghat…ôn pahrien. K…ôn it…®mat m…®n ekoat…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm net…ômim m…ôm…ô in et…ôm w…®r, k…ôn n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô it…®mat ioat…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn.\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Jon 19:35; 21:24\f*   
\s1 Namnun n…ôghat…ôn  
\p
\v 13 Iatos n…ôghat…ôn tep…ôt m…ôm…ô oek…ôte m…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm ik, m…ôto esolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô oek…ôte e pen,  
\v 14 m…ôto-inu n…®kik tat…ôht p…®k m…ôm…ô ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn ek…ôplan ik, k…ôn kilau ku…ôghat …ôtuat…®p k…ôm kilau m…®n.   
\p
\v 15 Iat…ôfak m…ôm…ô p…ôs Uhg…®n otasitu lam e n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn.\f + \fr 1:15 \ft Rom 1:7; Efes 6:23\f*  
\p Ik m…®n neen koat…ôn-ip…®n…ô ‚Äút…ôw…®r‚Äù k…ôm ik. K…ôn onak…ôn-ip…ôn ‚Äút…ôw…®r‚Äù r…ôhat…®mat k…ôm piatat m…®n neen ik…®n-un.   